normalise

public NormalisedModel normalise()
                          throws NormaliserException,
                                 Exception
General method to normalise the given problem- and parameter specification. Returns a normalised model containing normalised constraints, a list of parameters that have not yet been inserted (because they appear in unenrolled quantifications) and a list of decision variables and their corresponding domain.
